## Namespace 觀察

### 六種 namespace 用途（用自己的話）
- PID：Controls process visibility and container can only see its own processes
- NET：Provides isolated network stack (IP, port, routing table)
- MNT：Separates filesystem mount points
- UTS：Separates hostname/domain name
- IPC：Isolates inter-process communication
- USER：Maps user/group IDs for privilege isolation

