### 容器內 `ps aux` 輸出
Inside the container, ps aux shows only processes visible within the container's PID namespace.

Even though the host system has hundreds of processes, the container only sees processes belonging to the same namespace context.

This is why system processes like PID 1 exist inside the container, but host-level processes are mostly hidden.

